OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,FPubs, restaurants, cafes, bars and
OL,7,Flive music venues across Wales will
OL,8,Fget additional business rates support,
OL,9,Fthe Welsh Government has announced.
OL,11,FAround 4,400 hospitality businesses
OL,12,Fwill be eligible for 15% relief on
OL,13,Ftheir rates bills in 2026-27.
OL,15,FEligible businesses will be able to
OL,16,Fapply for the relief through their
OL,17,Flocal authority from April 2026.
