OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,FIt comes after news that pubs and
OL,7,Fmusic venues in England would be given
OL,8,Fa 15% discount on their business rates
OL,9,Fbills from April and will not see
OL,10,Fincreases for two years.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government said it is
OL,13,Fspending up to #8million on the
OL,14,Fpackage, using funding from the UK
OL,15,FGovernment but also deploying its own
OL,16,Ffunds to finance support which it says
OL,17,F"comes on top of substantial existing
OL,18,Fsupport".
