OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,FAlmost half of pubs in Wales currently
OL,7,Freceive Small Business Rates Relief,
OL,8,Fand more than a quarter pay no rates
OL,9,Fat all.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Government's permanent
OL,12,Freliefs are worth #250million every
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FFrom April, the multiplier used to
OL,16,Fwork out rates bills will also be
OL,17,Freduced for the first time since 2010,
OL,18,Fand #116million in transitional relief
OL,19,Fis being provided over two years to
OL,20,Fhelp businesses adjust to the
OL,21,Frevaluation.
