OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,FWelsh Liberal Democrat Leader Jane
OL,7,FDodds MS had called on the Labour-run
OL,8,FWelsh Government to urgently change
OL,9,Fcourse on business rates policy to
OL,10,Fprotect pubs and hospitality
OL,11,Fbusinesses across Wales.
OL,13,FWales' finance secretary Mark
OL,14,FDrakeford said: "Pubs, restaurants,
OL,15,Fcafes, bars, and live music venues are
OL,16,Fat the heart of communities across
OL,17,FWales. We know they are facing real
OL,18,Fpressures, from rising costs to
OL,19,Fchanging consumer habits.
