OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,F"This additional support will help
OL,7,Faround 4,400 businesses as they adapt
OL,8,Fto these challenges. We have extended
OL,9,Fthis relief to restaurants and cafes,
OL,10,Fas well as pubs and live music venues,
OL,11,Fbecause in towns and high streets
OL,12,Facross Wales these businesses operate
OL,13,Fside by side, often in direct
OL,14,Fcompetition. It makes sense to support
OL,15,Fthem equally.
