OL,3,CExtra rates relief for pubs and
OL,4,Crestaurants announced in Wales
OL,6,F"At a UK level, the Liberal Democrats
OL,7,Fhave called for an emergency cut to
OL,8,FVAT for the hospitality sector to help
OL,9,Fbusinesses survive this crisis. Here
OL,10,Fin Wales, the Welsh Government must
OL,11,Fplay its part by committing to
OL,12,Fpermanently extending and enhancing
OL,13,Fhospitality business rates relief.
OL,14,FWithout urgent action, we risk losing
OL,15,Fviable, well-loved businesses that
OL,16,Fcommunities across Wales simply cannot
OL,17,Fafford to lose."
